===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
In oracle bone script, {{Han compound|ls=ic|革|月|t1=change|t2=moon|nocap=yes}} – changes in moonlight.

Bronze inscriptions added {{och-l|*雨}} to make {{och-l|䨣}} a phonetic component.

